---

<section class="app-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="main-title md:hidden">
      Tu tatuaje, nuestra<br /> obra de arte
    </h1>

    <div class="cards-grid">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <img src="/img/app/11.png" alt="Serpiente" />
          <div class="icon-glow"></div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Servicios personalizados</h2>
        
        <p>
          Desde diseños personalizados hasta curación de heridas, ofrecemos una
          experiencia completa para que tu tatuaje sea una obra maestra.
        </p>
        
        <div class="card-highlight"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <img src="/img/app/10.png" alt="Lobo" />
          <div class="icon-glow"></div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Tatuajes para todos</h2>
        
        <p>
          Descubre una amplia variedad de estilos, desde tradicionales hasta
          modernos, y encuentra el que mejor se adapta a ti.
        </p>
        
        <div class="card-highlight"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="icon-wrapper">
          <img src="/img/app/5.png" alt="Unicornio" />
          <div class="icon-glow"></div>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Más allá del tatuaje</h2>
        
        <p>
          Además de nuestros servicios de tatuaje, ofrecemos productos de
          cuidado de la piel y asesoramiento para mantener tu tatuaje en
          perfectas condiciones.
        </p>
        
        <div class="card-highlight"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Imagen decorativa -->
    <div class="decorative-image">
      <div class="image-overlay"></div>
      <img src="/img/app/7.png" alt="Imagen decorativa" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .app-section {
    background-color: #141D3C;
    background-image: url('/img/Frame 7.png');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    position: relative;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .app-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      rgba(67, 24, 255, 0.1),
      transparent
    );
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .main-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(67, 24, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .cards-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(67, 24, 255, 0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(67, 24, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .icon-wrapper {
    position: relative;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .icon-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: contain;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .icon-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -50%;
    background: radial-gradient(
      circle at center,
      rgba(67, 24, 255, 0.3),
      transparent 70%
    );
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .icon-glow {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .feature-card h2 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .feature-card p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .card-highlight {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      45deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(67, 24, 255, 0.1),
      transparent
    );
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .card-highlight {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .decorative-image {
    position: absolute;
    right: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 40%;
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .decorative-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    opacity: 0.5;
    transform: scale(1.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to right,
      #141D3C,
      transparent
    );
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) {
    .feature-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(
        45deg,
        transparent,
        rgba(67, 24, 255, 0.3),
        transparent
      );
      mask: linear-gradient(#fff 0 0) content-box,
            linear-gradient(#fff 0 0);
      mask-composite: exclude;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .feature-card:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .decorative-image {
      display: none;
    }

    .cards-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>